      "text": [
        " قَالَ أَبُو عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) أَكْمَلُ النَّاسِ عَقْلًا أَحْسَنُهُمْ خُلُقاً ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ja’far Bin Muhammad Al Ashary, from Ubeydullah Al Dihqan, from Dorost, from Ibrahim Bin Abdul Hameed who said, ",
          "‘Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘The most perfect of the people in intellect, is the best of them in morals’."
        ]
